# Tu-Wane Jipps - Behind the scenes[]

Tu-Wane Jipps appeared in the comic story "Tales of Villainy: Credits," which was published in Star Wars Adventures (2020) 4 on March 24, 2021. The story was written by Jordan Clark and illustrated by Yael Nathan.
